class BenchmarkANFISTraining:
    def peakmem_training_epoch(self, n_samples):
        tracemalloc.start()
        self.model.fit(self.X, self.y)
        _, peak = tracemalloc.get_traced_memory()
        tracemalloc.stop()
        return peak

    def setup(self, n_samples):
        np.random.seed(42)
    
        # reproducible synthetic data
        self.X = np.random.rand(n_samples, 2)
        self.y = np.sum(self.X, axis=1)
    
        # default model
        self.model = ANFISRegressor(epochs=1)
